These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, nurse, pilot, security-guard, social-worker
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bluemaster, montecristo, siglo, ritmeester, blend
1. the pilot is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is between the social-worker and the davidoff-smoker##2
5. the siglo-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the bluemaster-smoker##2
6. the davidoff-smoker is the pilot##1
7. the security-guard is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the blend-smoker is on the left of the firefighter##1
9. the security-guard is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | analyst | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard | pilot    | nurse  |
| Cigar   | blend | bluemaster   | siglo       | ritmeester        | davidoff | montecristo |

