.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
House: futuristic, craftsman, cottage, gothic-revival, farmhouse, victorian
6 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the owner of the horse is between the gothic-revival house and the futuristic house##2
4. the cottage house is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
8. the craftsman house is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| House   | craftsman | victorian | farmhouse | gothic-revival | cottage | futuristic  |
| Pet           | snake | lizard  | frog | goat    | horse  | guinea-pig |

