.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different pets are kept: rat, snake, horse, guinea-pig, pony, dog
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the rat is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the dog##2
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Pet        | snake    | dog | horse | rat | pony | guinea-pig   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

