.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, trike, boat, helicopter, van
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, cycling, golf, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the helicopter##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Transport   | quad-bike   | boat    | van | trike | snowmobile | helicopter   |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | cycling | soccer | golf  | biathlon |

