.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, ship, quad-bike, trike, car
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the car##1
8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Transport    | helicopter | car | trike  | quad-bike      | ship | taxi  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

