.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, cola, coffee, milk, mirinda
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, gospel, indie, jazz, trance
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of trance is between the fan of jazz and the fan of blues##2
4. the person drinking coffee is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking milk##2
6. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage           | coffee | mirinda | milk | cola | iced-tea | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | indie   | disco         | blues    | trance     | jazz     |

