.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
City: colone, nizza, berlin, san-francisco, venice, edinburgh
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, skateboarding, skiing, soccer, surfing
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person traveling to colone and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| City   | colone   | venice  | nizza | san-francisco | edinburgh | berlin     |
| Sport   | sailing | biathlon | surfing    | soccer | skiing | skateboarding |

