3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the bird##2
9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Sport   | sailing | badminton | ice-hockey   | volleyball | tennis | water-polo |
| Pet           | bird  | pony   | goldfish | ferret | snake       | rabbit |

