 5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the jet-ski and the palace house##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the palace house##1
 8. the colonial house is the person driving the car##1
 9. the wooden house is between the person driving the car and the townhouse house##2
10. the colonial house is the person driving the car##1

