4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating apple##1
8. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
